----------------------------------------------------------------------
Blank court forms (NOT redistributed)
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The blank PDF forms this library maps are official documents of the
Maine Judicial Branch:

    https://www.courts.maine.gov/forms-fees-fines/forms.html

They are NOT included in or redistributed by this repository. Each form's
official `source_url` (forms/<ID>/form.yaml), together with a size and
SHA-256 in catalog/pdf_manifest.json, lets the tooling fetch and verify the
official blank on demand (see tools/fetch_pdfs.py).

The forms remain the property of the Maine Judicial Branch and are subject
to its terms; this project claims no rights over them. Any built artifact
that embeds a blank Maine Judicial Branch form should carry this attribution.

This repository's own work — code (engine/, tools/) and the structured form
artifacts (forms/<ID>/ metadata, schemas, skills, mappings; catalog/; docs/)
— is the part licensed under Apache-2.0.

Not legal advice. Filled output is a draft and must be verified against the
official form before filing.
